Description: Dynamic wallpaper changer with smooth transitions
 BoredNoMore3 is a sophisticated wallpaper management daemon for
 Debian-based distributions. It provides smooth, ImageMagick-powered
 transitions across environments like GNOME, KDE, XFCE, Cinnamon, and MATE.
 .
 Features:
  - 1000+ built-in transition effects using ImageMagick distortions
  - Universal desktop environment support (GNOME, KDE, XFCE, LXQt, MATE, etc.)
  - Professional CustomTkinter GUI (borednomore3-gui)
  - Command-line backend daemon (borednomore3)
  - Configurable intervals and transition parameters
  - Wallpaper downloader utility
  - Debug mode for troubleshooting
  - True random shuffle with no repeats until full cycle
 .
 The package includes both a backend daemon for automated wallpaper
 rotation and a modern GUI frontend for easy configuration and monitoring.
